<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> matiraiyum Īḻamum koṇṭa koppara<unclear>k</unclear>ecaripanmaṟki yāṇṭu <num value="41">4 <g type="numeral">10</g> 1</num>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>āvatu Aruvānāṭṭu mivaḻi vāvalūrnāṭṭu tevatāṉam tiruvāmāttūr Ūruṭaiya <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>va<hi rend="grantha"/>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rkku tañcāvūrkkūṟ<supplied reason="omitted">ṟa</supplied>ttu tañcāvūr Āṉainaṭaiyan pūtañ cilaiyan makaṉ cilaiyan vaṭukan vaiy
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tta nontāviḷakku 1- ṟukku poṉa patiṉkaḻañcu yitu <hi rend="grantha">śantrādi</hi> ttaval Erippatāka <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi> yum Ūrum <hi rend="grantha">de</hi>va<hi rend="grantha"/>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṉ coṟṟuṇai Akamuṭaiyāḷ ceṭṭaṅkai vaitta tirunontāviḷakku Oṉṟukku vaitta poṉ patiṉkaḻañcu Ippoṉ patiṉkaḻañcuṅ koṇṭu Ittiruviḷakku Oṉṟum <hi rend="grantha">cantrādi</hi> ttaval Erikka<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>kaṭavār <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
</p>

